"title": "8231: discipline, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8231: discipline, divine",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God disciplines his people through his word, through their experiences and through punishment, so that they may live in ways pleasing to him.</p>\n<h2>The nature of God's discipline</h2>\n<h3>It is a sign of God's love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:6\">HEB 12:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:12\">PRO 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:75\">PSA 119:75</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:19\">REV 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>It is a sign of belonging to God's family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:6\">HEB 12:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:12\">PRO 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:5\">DEU 8:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:14\">2SA 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:7\">HEB 12:7</a></p>\n<h3>It trains God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:11\">HEB 12:11</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The means of God's discipline</h2>\n<h3>The use of Scripture</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:36\">DEU 4:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:29\">DEU 29:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:11\">ISA 8:11</a></p>\n<h3>The knowledge of God's grace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11-Titus2:12\">TIT 2:11–2:12</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Instructive experiences</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:1-Deut8:5\">DEU 8:1–8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:2-Deut11:7\">DEU 11:2–11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:12\">PSA 90:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:17\">ISA 48:17</a></p>\n<h3>Painful experiences</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:7\">HEB 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:7–12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5\">HEB 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:11\">HEB 12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:6-1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:6–1:7</a></p>\n<h3>Punishment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:6\">HEB 12:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:12\">PRO 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:18\">LEV 26:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:21\">LEV 26:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:23-Lev26:24\">LEV 26:23–26:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:27-Lev26:28\">LEV 26:27–26:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:14\">2SA 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:14\">PSA 73:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:19\">JER 32:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:2\">HOS 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:15-Hos7:16\">HOS 7:15–7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:32\">1CO 11:32</a></p>\n<h2>God disciplines all and only his children</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:8\">HEB 12:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:6\">HEB 12:6</a></p>\n<h2>The goals of God's discipline</h2>\n<h3>Respectful submission to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:9\">HEB 12:9</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The good of God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:10\">HEB 12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:17-Job5:18\">JOB 5:17–5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:12\">PSA 94:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:67\">PSA 119:67</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:71\">PSA 119:71</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:75\">PSA 119:75</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual growth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:11\">HEB 12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:2-Prov1:3\">PRO 1:2–1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Preparation for heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17-2Cor4:18\">2CO 4:17–4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18\">ROM 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a></p>\n<h2>Believers should not despise God's discipline</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:17\">JOB 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5\">HEB 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:11\">PRO 3:11</a></p>\n<h2>Divine discipline in the church</h2>\n<h3>By reproof</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:8\">2CO 7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:2\">2CO 13:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:15\">2TH 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>For the benefit of sinners</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:15\">MAT 18:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:1-1Cor5:7\">1CO 5:1–5:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:14\">2TH 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>As a warning to others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:20\">1TI 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>To be exercised with kindness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:6\">2CO 2:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1\">GAL 6:1</a></p>\n<h3>The role of witnesses</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:16\">MAT 18:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:19\">1TI 5:19</a></p>",
